column5: I have three weeks between trips and need a safe place to park my 16 ft. boat. Empty garage or outside would be fine. The boat will be covered. Do not want to haul it home 700 miles and then haul it back up again. Anyone ??Thanks,Tom
Tom, We have similar problems. We leave our boats in Orr, Minn at Rays marina. They are the only boat place in town and very reasonable. Good luck.
Hey Crawler Catcher,Email me at [email protected] I have 2 places in the Falls that you could park your boat at for a couple of weeks.Matt
Does anyone have any place that they would recommend storing a boat in the International Falls area?ThanksDan
